Pomodoro project:

Window:
    init window
    define size
    define title

Tkinter:
    Start button:
        when clicked, starts timer counting down from 25:00 to 0

    Reset button:
        reset "pomodoros" (25 minute work sessions)

    Timer:
        25:00 timer, when reaching 0, focus on pomodoro window, add checkmark to signify one "round" completed
         and start new timer counting down from 5:00




